# Build context lives at the repo root (web/Dockerfile uses context: .).
# Exclude everything that must not leak into the build, especially nested
# node_modules whose symlinks would collide with the fresh pnpm store.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/*.pyc
.git
.env
.env.local
.github
node_modules
